Additional Software &daps-addon;
Directory Structure
For &dapsacr; to work out of the box, it requires a certain organization of your DocBook XML files and images within your documentation directory. For details, refer to . You can generate the necessary structure with the &dapsacr; initialization script, daps-init. For instructions on how to make existing DocBook projects compatible with &dapsacr;, refer to .

