Installing and Configuring the FO Formatter
For installation and configuration of an FO formatter (for generating PDF output), refer to its installation instructions (or to your system administrator). For FOP, you usually only need to install the respective FOP package. However, not all FOP packages contain hyphenation pattern files. taroth 2012-03-26: todo - mention download from offo.sourceforeg.net in troubleshooting section and add xref

